CCH:

"A co-operative and mutual housing scheme has a community membership where those who live in homes developed are required or are encouraged to become members – in some cases – alongside other local community members. That community membership is able to democratically control the housing organisation in some way through general meetings of the organisation."
(http://www.cch.coop/what-is-co-operative-and-mutual-housing/)

